scenes.description: FUWAMOCO performs a cover of 'Let's Go! Onmyoji' with Marine and Miko.
MC segment where FUWAMOCO discusses the performance and reveals their birthday merchandise.

subtitles.english: Uuuuuuuuuu...
In times of pain, in times of sadness...
In moments like those, darkness forms in the gaps of the heart.
Into that darkness, monsters will crawl in without mercy!
So even if it's painful, do not falter!
Do not be depressed! Do not dwell on it!
A resilient heart that never gives in to anything...
...is the ultimate weapon of all!
Loneliness preys on a wavering heart...
...a heart being targeted.
Smash it to pieces!
Evil spirits, begone! Evil spirits, begone!
When you're troubled by paranormal phenomena...
Doman! Seman! Doman! Seman!
Let the Onmyoji exorcise them! Let's go!

BAU BAU! Hi!
